{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I gave this ration to this Ruskie, and there must have been six people, I suppose, in this party, and this was one ration from me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he broke it up and gave each piece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was humiliating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they told me how they'd been treated, and I was livid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had no idea that people could do this sort of thing to one another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anyway--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How they're being treated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the first time I'd spoken to people in concentration camp uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were the very first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, I can't remember the details of it now, they were beaten with rifle butts and all this sort of thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember the exact phrasing after 50 years, but I do remember that they described it very effectively as they're using the rifle butt like this, and the boot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew these things, but we didn't-- had no idea that this sort of thing was done.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Women, children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], if you know French soldiers' catchwords.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were filthy beyond words, but they'd had the guts and the energy to get ashore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So whether they were injured or not, you know, they were-- were in a terrible mess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anyway, I told them to go back to Lubeck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, there's no good coming with us because we can't carry you, but you must go back to Lubeck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I said, in Lubeck, very soon you'll see a vehicle with a sign, with a shield, and it will say, 'Red Shield.' now that's the Salvation Army welfare truck.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, if you see this truck with a-- or a house or a flag with a shield, and it says on it, 'Red Shield Salvation Army,' go to that vehicle.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
